behavior and interests. Similarly, enterprising 
organizations have been data mining social 
analytics of the bitcoin blockchain since 
inception. Therefore, it should be no surprise 
that most Bitcoin clients provide user options 
like conducting secure transactions via the Tor 
network. Developers of Tor say that “by 
routing tra�c over Tor, no one learns the 
origin IP address of Alice when she performs 
the bitcoin transaction." Some Bitcoin wallets 
support and use Tor, such as Electrum and 
Armory.

