Bitcoin Substantially Dominates the Cryptocurrency Market

TPAY is entirely based on the omnipresent Bitcoin. In a large, global survey by 
the University of Cambridge, all 51 exchanges surveyed listed Bitcoin. The 
second most popular, Ether, is far behind being listed on only 43% of all 
exchanges. As well, Bitcoin is the most widely used payment rail for 
cross-border transactions.

