experience financial di�culty. 
There are some ways that 
TokenPay could reach this point: 
not enough funds raised 
through the token sale or the 
popularity of the BlueDiamond 
debit card reaches such a 
critical mass that the 
“cash-back” TPAY rewards 
cannot be adequately funded.

Ensure a workable, 
dynamically adjusted, 
financial model that makes 
adequate provisions for 
credits over di�erent 
scenarios of users and 
usage patterns of the debit 
card. Adjust fees and/or 
credits accordingly to 
ensure a viable capital 
adequacy strategy.

Technology This is the TokenPay core 
strength, but could also be a 
liability. Tor network nodes 
could be hacked and expose our 
customers IP addresses, hence, 
compromise our technology 
promises for confidentiality and 
privacy. 

Ensure that the technology 
roadmap, vision, and 
capacity remains ahead of 
the curve. Engage with the 
development community 
and always make sure that 
TokenPay has the latest 
patches, and updates. Use 
of the latest techniques to 
ensure confidentiality and 
privacy of customers 
accounts (nodes) are 
preserved within the 
permitted limits of the law.

